Your minimum deck size is 75 cards. Your deck cannot include more than 1 copy of each attachment .&nbsp;
<b>Action:</b> Kneel your faction card and pay X gold to put an attachment with printed cost X into play from your hand.
<b>Reaction:</b> After an attachment enters play under your control, either: draw a card or gain 1 gold. (Limit 3 times per round.)
